  "prompt": "Which are the best IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi?",
  "response": "As of my last update, several IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi have gained a strong reputation based on student reviews and success rates. Here are some of the top choices:\n\n1. **British Council** - Known for its experienced faculty and comprehensive course material. They offer various programs tailored to individual needs.\n\n2. **Jamboree Education** - Offers extensive training for IELTS with a focus on personalized attention and practice tests.\n\n3. **Manya \u2013 The Princeton Review** - Provides structured training programs and has a good track record of helping students achieve high scores.\n\n4. **Fateh Education** - Specializes in IELTS coaching with a strong emphasis on preparation and practice exams.\n\n5. **Megamind** - Known for its dedicated faculty, flexible class timings, and customized study plans.\n\n6. **Plutus Academy** - Offers a mix of online and offline classes with a well-structured curriculum and practice resources.\n\n7. **Cambridge English Academy** - Focuses on all facets of the IELTS exam with interactive coaching sessions.\n\nKeep in mind that the best choice might depend on your specific needs, such as location, budget, batch size, and teaching style. It\u2019s advisable to visit these institutes, if possible, attend a demo class, and speak with current or former students to make an informed decision.",
